@sessionId = fd371479-2ac5-4096-b194-b45a5c4db7fc

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WebSocket (Socket.io) — cannot be tested with REST Client.
# Connect to:  ws://localhost:6969/sessions
#
# Handshake authentication — pass JWT in the auth object:
#   { auth: { token: "<accessToken>" } }
#
# On connect the server automatically emits sessionResume if a session is
# in-flight in Redis (crash recovery).
#
# Client → Server events:
#
#   startSession      { taskId: string }
#   heartbeat         { sessionId: string }          ← emit every 30s
#   logDistraction    { sessionId, reason, estimatedMinutes }
#   stopSession       { sessionId: string }
#
# Server → Client events:
#
#   sessionStarted    { sessionId, serverStartedAt, taskEstimatedDurationMinutes }
#   heartbeatAck      { elapsedMs, plantGrowthPercent }
#   distractionLogged { distractions[], plantStatus }
#   sessionStopped    { sessionId, durationMinutes, netFocusMinutes,
#                       distractionCount, plantStatus, plantGrowthPercent, completedAt }
#   sessionResume     { sessionId, elapsedMs, taskId,
#                       taskEstimatedDurationMinutes, plantGrowthPercent }
#   error             { message }
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ─── REST: Manual time entry ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### POST — log manual session (no timer, no WebSocket)
# @name manualSession
POST {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{sessionsPath}}/manual
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "taskId": "{{taskId}}",
  "durationMinutes": 45,
  "startedAt": "2026-02-27T09:00:00.000Z",
  "note": "Deep work on algorithm design"
}

###
@manualSessionId = PASTE_MANUAL_SESSION_ID_HERE

# ─── REST: Session history ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET all sessions for a task
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{sessionsPath}}/task/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET single session by ID
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{sessionsPath}}/{{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── Error cases ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### ❌ POST manual — missing durationMinutes (should return 400)
POST {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{sessionsPath}}/manual
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "taskId": "{{taskId}}"
}

###

### ❌ POST manual — invalid taskId (should return 404)
POST {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{sessionsPath}}/manual
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "taskId": "000000000000000000000000",
  "durationMinutes": 30
}

###

### ❌ GET session without token (should return 401)
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{sessionsPath}}/{{sessionId}}

###

### ❌ GET non-existent session (should return 404)
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{sessionsPath}}/nonexistent-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
